   400	| ------------ | ------------------------- | ------------------------- | ------------------------- |
   401	| `ArrowRight` | Focus next item           | Focus previous item       | --                        |
   402	| `ArrowLeft`  | Focus previous item       | Focus next item           | --                        |
   403	| `ArrowDown`  | --                        | --                        | Focus next item           |
   404	| `ArrowUp`    | --                        | --                        | Focus previous item       |
